%h3 (Note: Only first row has real time data, rest are random numbers but we can get real data once we set road extremities)
%table
  %tr
    %th Road Name
    %th Road Width(m)
    %th No. of Lanes
    %th Upstream Traffic Time
    %th Downstream Traffic Time
    %th Suggested Upstream lanes
    %th Suggested Downstream lanes
  - @roads.each do |road|
    - data = road.all_data
    %tr
      %td= road.name
      %td= road.width
      %td= road.get_lanes
      %td= data[:timings][0] 
      %td= data[:timings][1] 
      %td= data[:suggested_lanes][0] 
      %td= data[:suggested_lanes][1]